Thank you for the effort, but I must be honest: this video is shit. Don't get me wrong, the image quality is fine and the file is not corrupt or anything, but this is some of the lamest footage I've seen.

In each of about six scenes, the camera is across the room from an ok looking stripper who dances a little bit. There is no benefit to the 3d because the girls are so far away, it might as well be extremely lame 2d soft porn. I might keep it as a novelty, but I won't waste peoples time by seeding it.

It's side by side 3d, so plays with sView.
